---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const locale = 'es';
---

<Layout 
  title="Gaia Market | El Sistema Circulatorio"
  description="El marketplace donde cada transacción nutre al ecosistema. Productos, servicios, experiencias y conocimiento regenerativo."
  keywords={["Gaia Market", "marketplace regenerativo", "economía regenerativa", "productos sostenibles", "servicios regenerativos", "experiencias conscientes"]}
  schemaType={["WebPage", "Organization"]}
>
  
  <!-- Top Navigation Shell -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#fefee5]/80 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-[0_40px_60px_-5px_rgba(54,59,16,0.06)]">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center max-w-[1618px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] h-24">
      <a href="/es/" class="text-3xl font-black text-primary px-6 font-headline tracking-tight">
        Gaia
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-12 font-headline tracking-tight font-bold uppercase text-sm">
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/">Inicio</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/hub">Hub</a>
        <a class="text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1" href="/es/market">Market</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/es/commons">Commons</a>
        <div class="relative group">
          <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors flex items-center gap-1" href="/es/commons">
            Impact
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">expand_more</span>
          </a>
          <div class="absolute top-full left-0 pt-2 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200">
            <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-outline/10 py-2 min-w-[180px]">
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-on-surface/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/es/commons/impact-fund/">Impact Fund</a>
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-on-surface/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/es/commons/impact-hub/">Impact Hub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#comunidad" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-headline font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider hover:opacity-90 transition-all scale-95 active:scale-90">
          Únete
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-32">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] max-w-[1618px] mx-auto mb-32">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.618fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-secondary-container/50 text-secondary font-semibold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
            El Motor de la Regeneración
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black font-headline text-on-surface leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter">
            Donde cada compra <span class="text-primary italic">regenera</span> el mundo.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface/60 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-light">
            Un marketplace donde el dinero fluye hacia donde la vida lo necesita. Un sistema circulatorio que nutre el planeta mientras tú prosperas.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
            <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-10 py-5 rounded-full solar-gradient text-white font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase shadow-2xl hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-all text-center">
              Entrar al Marketplace
            </a>
            <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-10 py-5 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-surface-container transition-all text-center">
              Registrarme como Proveedor
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-primary-container/20 blur-3xl rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary-container/30 transition-all duration-700"></div>
          <img 
            alt="Regenerative Garden" 
            class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.02]" 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Statement -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto text-center space-y-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-headline max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
          El dinero que gastas define el mundo que construyes. <span class="text-secondary-dim">Gaia Market</span> es la alternativa.
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-16 text-left">
          <div class="space-y-4 p-8 bg-white rounded-xl ethereal-shadow">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">token</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-headline uppercase">Transparencia Radical</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 font-light">Trazabilidad total de cada moneda. Mira exactamente cómo tu compra impacta el suelo, el agua y las personas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 p-8 bg-white rounded-xl ethereal-shadow">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">eco</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-headline uppercase">Calidad Ancestral</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 font-light">Solo productos y servicios que devuelven más de lo que toman. Estándares regenerativos estrictos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 p-8 bg-white rounded-xl ethereal-shadow">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">group</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-headline uppercase">Economía Local</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 font-light">Eliminamos intermediarios parasitarios. La riqueza se queda en la comunidad que la crea.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Exchange Ecosystem (Bento Grid) -->
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold font-headline mb-6">Explora el Ecosistema</h2>
        <div class="h-1 w-32 bg-primary rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <!-- Products -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 lg:mb-12">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary">local_mall</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/40">01 / Productos</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Productos de la Tierra</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface/70 max-w-md">Alimentos orgánicos, artesanías con alma y objetos diseñados para durar mil años.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 lg:mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-secondary-container/50 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">BIO-COSECHA</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-secondary-container/50 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">ARTESANÍA VIVA</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Services -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 lg:mb-12">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-secondary-dim">handshake</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/40">02 / Servicios</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Servicios Conscientes</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/70">Consultoría regenerativa, terapias holísticas y soporte profesional alineado con la vida.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Knowledge -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-between group hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
          <div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 lg:mb-12">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-primary-dim">menu_book</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface/40">03 / Sabiduría</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Conocimiento</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/70">Cursos de permacultura, economía sagrada y talleres de autogestión.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Experiences -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8 relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden group min-h-[300px] lg:min-h-[400px]">
          <img 
            alt="Experiences" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953e39b3ac?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-on-surface/80 to-transparent p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-end">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60 mb-4">04 / Experiencias</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Retiros y Encuentros</h3>
            <p class="text-white/80 max-w-sm">Reconecta con la red de la vida en santuarios regenerativos alrededor del globo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Cycle: Solar Alchemy Visualization -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-24">
          <span class="text-primary font-headline font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sm">Alquimia Solar</span>
          <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mt-6">El Ciclo de la Vida</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative z-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 solar-gradient rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 lg:mb-8 shadow-2xl">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-3xl lg:text-4xl" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">shopping_cart</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-3">Compra</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm px-2">Tu intercambio inicia el flujo energético en el ecosistema.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative z-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 lg:mb-8 shadow-xl border-4 border-primary-container">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl lg:text-4xl">percent</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-3">Comisión</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm px-2">Una fracción se destina automáticamente al bien común.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative z-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 bg-secondary-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 lg:mb-8 shadow-xl">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl lg:text-4xl">account_balance</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-3">Tesoro Común</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm px-2">Fondos custodiados colectivamente para regeneración.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="relative z-10 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 bg-tertiary-container rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 lg:mb-8 shadow-xl">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-3xl lg:text-4xl">eco</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-headline text-lg lg:text-xl font-bold mb-3">Inversión Regenerativa</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm px-2">El capital retorna a la tierra en forma de proyectos vitales.</p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Connecting Lines (Visual Decor) -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 lg:top-12 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-outline/30 to-transparent -z-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- User Profiles: Bento Grid -->
    <section class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] py-24 lg:py-32 max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 lg:mb-20">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-4">Para quién es</h2>
        <div class="w-32 h-2 solar-gradient rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-8 auto-rows-[300px]">
        <!-- Producers -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7 relative group rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high">
          <img 
            alt="Artisan pottery maker" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-40 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700" 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1459156212016-c812468e2115?q=80&w=2050&auto=format&fit=crop"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-on-surface/80 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8 lg:p-12 text-white">
            <span class="bg-primary px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-headline font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 inline-block">Creadores</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Productores</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-lg opacity-80 max-w-md">Ofrece tus productos a una red que valora lo regenerativo.</p>
            <button class="mt-8 flex items-center font-headline font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Registrarme <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2">arrow_forward</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Professionals -->
        <div class="md:col-span-5 relative group rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-surface-container">
          <img 
            alt="Collaborative team meeting" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-40 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-700" 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-on-surface/80 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 p-8 lg:p-12 text-white">
            <span class="bg-tertiary px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-headline font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 inline-block">Expertos</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Profesionales</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-base opacity-80">Comparte tus servicios con quienes los necesitan.</p>
            <button class="mt-6 flex items-center font-headline font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">
              Ofrecer servicios <span class="material-symbols-outlined ml-2">arrow_forward</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Communities -->
        <div class="md:col-span-12 relative group rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-secondary-container">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
            <span class="text-[15vw] font-black text-secondary/10 select-none leading-none">COMUNIDAD</span>
          </div>
          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center p-8 lg:p-16">
            <div>
              <span class="bg-secondary-dim text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-headline font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 inline-block">Colectivos</span>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-secondary-dim mb-6">Comunidades</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-lg lg:text-xl text-secondary-dim/80 leading-relaxed mb-8">Accede a todo lo que necesitas, alineado con tus valores. Ecovillas, DAOs y cooperativas intercambiando recursos.</p>
              <button class="bg-secondary-dim text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform">Registrar colectivo</button>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <img 
                class="rounded-xl aspect-square object-cover shadow-2xl" 
                alt="Community gathering" 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529156069898-49953e39b3ac?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop"
              />
              <img 
                class="rounded-xl aspect-square object-cover shadow-2xl mt-12" 
                alt="Shared vegetable garden" 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section id="comunidad" class="py-24 lg:py-40 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] max-w-[1618px] mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter mb-8 lg:mb-12 leading-none">
        Otro modelo económico <br/> <span class="text-primary italic">ya está funcionando.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 lg:gap-8 mt-12 lg:mt-16">
        <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-12 lg:px-16 py-6 lg:py-8 rounded-full solar-gradient text-white font-headline font-black text-lg tracking-widest uppercase shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all text-center">
          Entrar al Marketplace
        </a>
        <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="px-12 lg:px-16 py-6 lg:py-8 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface font-headline font-black text-lg tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-surface-container transition-all text-center">
          Registrarme como Proveedor
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-10 lg:mt-12 text-on-surface/50 font-light tracking-wide uppercase text-sm">Únete a más de 450 comunidades regenerativas hoy.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="w-full py-[5.5rem] bg-surface-container">
    <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.618fr_1fr] gap-12 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="font-headline font-bold text-primary text-2xl tracking-tight">
          Gaia Ecosystem
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/60 max-w-sm">
          Infraestructura para una civilización regenerativa. Un ecosistema descentralizado de coordinación planetaria.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface/40">
          © 2026 Gaia Ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 font-body text-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Explorar</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/hub">Gaia Hub</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/market">Gaia Market</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/es/commons">Gaia Commons</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Comunidad</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank">Telegram</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
  }
  .solar-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #776300 0%, #ffd709 100%);
  }
  .ethereal-shadow {
    box-shadow: 0 40px 60px -5px rgba(54, 59, 16, 0.06);
  }
</style>
